Title: ucd_mem, hr_mem: Fixed wrong preferring of ucd_mem
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
Version: 1.4.0p31
Date: 1523540816
Class: fix

In december 2017 a bug has been introduced which lead into using ucd_mem
instead of using hr_mem anymore. This leads to vanished services which has
been created by hr_mem and new services created by ucd_mem.
This has now been fixed.
